WEBVTT

00:12:26.983 --> 00:12:33.983
If we can reduce the number
of viewers and clicks on any subject,

00:12:34.007 --> 00:12:37.433
the media will change
the way they report on it.

00:12:38.313 --> 00:12:43.501
So the next time you see
any media organization --

00:12:43.525 --> 00:12:47.818
print, digital, radio or television --

00:12:47.842 --> 00:12:54.320
gratuitously leveraging the names
and images of these shooters,

00:12:54.344 --> 00:12:55.505
stop watching,

00:12:56.406 --> 00:12:58.062
stop listening,

00:12:58.086 --> 00:12:59.930
stop clicking,

00:12:59.954 --> 00:13:01.532
stop liking